        Edit on GitHub
      </a>
    </StorySection>

    <StorySection
      theme="red"
      bgImage={vaultBg}
      label="Shared Resources"
      heading="Projects"
      body="Work at SuperBenefit is carried out by its cells; A purpose-aligned network of small, autonomous teams. We coordinate our cells as needed to share capacity and costs as a collaborative commons."
      posts={projects}
      variant="compact"
      basePath="/projects"
    >
      <p class="story-cta-blurb">Cells are self-organized as SuperBenefit DAO LLC, a translocal non-profit legally domiciled in the Marshall Islands.</p>
      <a href="/projects" class="story-btn story-btn--primary">
        <svg class="btn-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h5l2 3h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
